entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa ou di, ou gen pwoblèm pwoteje tèt ou?" t="怎么？你没有求生本能啊？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou gad tèt ou nan glasf? Ou fout sanble yon vye lobey san valè." t="你自己照过镜子没？你瞧着可悲死了。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou pa fè pati isit la." t="这不是你该待的地方。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fwenk, demaske w devan m lan! Touswit!" t="转过身，快滚蛋！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ale, fout ban mwen yon rezon!" t="来啊，来教训我啊！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ranje kò w, mete gran moun sou ou, ou tande m?" t="别乱动，你不是孩子了，听见了吗？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se avè map pale, wi!" t="我警告你！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen touye malandren ki pi gwo nèg pase w" t="比你屌的混球我都杀过！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se sa." t="这就对了。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Konsaaa menm menm." t="就是这样。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Hen?" t="嗯？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tonnè kriboul mwen." t="我真见鬼了。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Hm,ann ret veyatif, nou tande?" t="嗯，一定要保持警惕，明白了？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Bon, mwen fè de twa mouvman." t="至少我松了松筋骨。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Salopri a pa lwen non, m ka santi l!" t="那王八就在附近，我都感觉到了！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Parèt non, Fè m wè figi w." t="快出来，让我看看你的脸。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen jwenn yon kadav!" t="发现一具尸体！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Wi." t="明白。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ba w moso ladan l? Hen?" t="你是自己找死啊？嗯？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Map fout fini ou!" t="我送你上天！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Men pou nou!" t="接着吧！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Manzè tou pre a! Fout kraze bounda l!" t="她就在这里！干死她！" b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Monsieur tou pre a! Fout kraze bounda!" t="他就在这里！干死他！" b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Ki pwoblèm? Annik touye salopri a!" t="等什么呢？快杀了那婊子！" b="" a=""/>
entries.maleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Ki pwoblèm? Annik touye enbesil a non!" t="等什么呢？快杀了那傻狗！" b="" a=""/>

entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa gen katouch ankò!" t="我没子弹了！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Gade yon manman lobey!" t="真混蛋！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Med. Neg nan deyò." t="这帮外地人。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa w fout vle?" t="你干嘛？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Hen?" t="什么事？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou pa ka pale avè m jan... Mwen di ou ... Ou panse mwen pa konnen kote ou rete...?" t="你不能这么跟我说话…我告诉你…你真觉得我不知道你住哪儿…？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ki fout mele dada m, Mwen vle lavironndede m yo... Mwen konnen se betize wap betize avè m...!" t="我才不在乎，我要钱…我知道你在耍我…！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Annavan, Pouse'l!" t="围起来，快！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Map fè tou sa mwen ka fe la a!" t="我正努力呢！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Abrite bounda nou!" t="快找掩护！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tann lè mwen fout rele nou." t="我还在等电话呢。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Toujou gen yon salopri pou gade." t="，总要出点事。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="'Ey, 'ey, 'ey, vini la, ann al gade sa ki genyen." t="喂，喂，喂，快来，我们去查看一下。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Si nou wè yon bagay, annik tire. Pa rete ranse. Oke?" t="只要有丁点动静，就立马开枪。都精神点，明白？" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sa na p fout tannn?! Annavan!" t="你等啥呢？！快走啊！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen vle li vivan e ap rele!" t="我要活捉他，让他生不如死！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Aaghh…Li pi …...bon..si w..touye mwen... Ale w ….. Lan... mèd... " t="啊啊…你…最好…杀了我…去死吧你…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Bon, ou pa yon ti jan glise  ..." t="哎呀，你可真是个小滑头啊…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Kounye a si w te ka koute mwen fini..." t="好了，这回你可以把话听完了吧…" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen pa ka pase tout jounen an sou sa." t="我没功夫和你兜圈子。" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se sa... Kiyès ki swa kounyen an, Hen? Hahahaha!" t="这就对了…你可真是个乖崽崽啊，嗯？哈哈哈哈！" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Si mwen pa jwenn li demen, map pran tout done w yo epiii... O, Mwen deja gen sa yo ... Dakò..." t="要是我明天还没收到，我拿走你所有的数据，然后我…哦，我已经有数据了…好吧…" b="" a=""/>
